<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note14" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Diodorus_Siculus/17F*.html#ref14
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">14</A>
This story is not otherwise told in this connection, but is of a type which is located in northern Iran. Onesicritus (Jacoby, <I>Fragmente der Griechische Historiker</I>, no. 134, F 5;
	<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Strabo/11K*.html#11.3
	"TARGET="Strabo_E"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,Strabo,WIDTH,195)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
Strabo, 11.11.3</A>) told that the Bactrians and Sogdians threw out their sick and elderly to be devoured by dogs, but that Alexander stopped the practice. Plutarch twice refers to this institution. In
	<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Moralia/Fortuna_Alexandri*/2.html#we_love_our_parents_in_different_ways
	"TARGET="Plutarch_E"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,Plutarch,WIDTH,PlutarchWidth)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
<I>De Fortuna aut Virtute Alexandri</I>, 1.5, 328<SPAN CLASS="small">C</SPAN></A>, he says that Sogdians kill their parents, while the Scythians eat them. In
	<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Moralia/An_vitiositas_ad_infelicitatem_sufficiat*.html#Theodorus
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,0,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
<I>Can Vice Cause Unhappiness?</I> 3, 499<SPAN CLASS="small">D</SPAN></A>, he reports that the dead were devoured by dogs among the Hyrcanians, and by birds among the Bactrians (also
	<A HREF="
http://www.thelatinlibrary.com/cicero/tusc1.shtml#108
	"TARGET="offsite"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,LatinRef2,WIDTH,195)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
Cicero, <I>Disp. Tusc.</I> 1.45.108</A>). For other instances cp. Strabo, 11.11.<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Strabo/11K*.html#11.3
	"TARGET="Strabo_E"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,Strabo,WIDTH,195)"
onMouseOut="nd();">3 <SPAN CLASS="small">(517)</SPAN></A>;
	<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Strabo/11K*.html#11.8
	"TARGET="Strabo_E"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,Strabo,WIDTH,195)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
8 <SPAN CLASS="small">(520)</SPAN></A>; 15.1.<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Strabo/15A3*.html#1.56
	"TARGET="Strabo_E"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,Strabo,WIDTH,195)"
