<SPAN CLASS="whole">Twenty-seven</SPAN> feet. Cp. Arrian, <I>Indica</I>, 30.8<!--</A>ARRIAN:INDICA-->.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
