	"TARGET="Curtius"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,LatinRef1,WIDTH,155)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
Curtius, 9.10.19</A>. Leonnatus was later crowned for a victory on this occasion
(Arrian, 7.5.5)<!--</A>ARRIAN7-->.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note22" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Diodorus_Siculus/17F*.html#ref22
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
