	"TARGET="Plutarch_E"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,Plutarch,WIDTH,PlutarchWidth)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
Plutarch, <I>Alexander</I>, 73.1‑2</A>;
Arrian, 7.16.5‑18.6<!--</A>ARRIAN7-->.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note57" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Diodorus_Siculus/17F*.html#ref57
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">57</A>
Arrian
(7.17.1‑4)
	<!--</A>ARRIAN7-->
makes the reverse statement, that the priests wanted to keep the revenues of the temple of Bel to themselves.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note58" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Diodorus_Siculus/17F*.html#ref58
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
